stment management solutions it offers investment management services including investment selection internal strategies manager access and alternative investment and wealth advisory services including fiduciary stable flexible trustee planning resource family advisor and philanthropic legacy the company was founded in  and is based in boston massachusetts atlantic trust company na a private wealth management company provides integrated wealth management services for high net worth individuals families foundations and endowments the company considers clients’ financial trust estate planning and philanthropic needs in developing customized asset allocation and investment management solutions it offers investment management services including investment selection internal strategies manager access and alternative investment and wealth advisory services including fiduciary stable flexible trustee planning resource family advisor and philanthropic legacy the company was founded in  and is based in boston massachusetts with locations in atlanta austin baltimore boston chicago denver houston new york newport beach san francisco washington and wilmington it also has offices in west palm beach florida and austin houston and dallas texas atlantic trust company na operates as a subsidiary of atlantic trust group llc detailed description  federal streetth floorboston ma united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwatlantictrustcom key executives for atlantic trust company na mr john sheehan markwalter jr chairman and chief executive officer mr eric brown propper cfa president and chief operating officer mr jeffrey scott thomas cfa vice chairman and managing director of boston ms denise c whennen senior vice president and business development officer mr barry n berlin cfa managing director of wealth management at atlanta compensation as of fiscal year  atlantic trust company na key developments atlantic trust opens new office in dallas john w winslow to serve as head of the dallas office jun   atlantic trust has increased the firms national reach with the opening of its dallas office the firms th location this strategic expansion builds upon the firms success in texas with its established houston and austin offices the new office is located at  crescent court in uptown dallas managing director john w winslow cfa will serve as head of the dallas office winslow has more than  years of industry experience working with clients to provide holistic wealth management solutions to suit their individual needs atlantic trust company na relocates headquarters mar   atlantic trust co na relocated its headquarters from midtown atlanta to the citys buckhead neighborhood it moved its headquarters to the forum at  northside parkway which provides room for growth as the firm looks to expand its presence in the southeast region atlantic trust relocates headquarters announces executive changes mar   atlantic trust announced that it has relocated its headquarters office from midtown atlanta to the citys buckhead neighborhood the new headquarters office in buckhead is located at the forum at  northside parkway which provides room for growth as the firm looks to expand its presence in the southeast region barry n berlin cfa and w scott thompson iii managing directors and coheads of the atlanta office says the firm chose the buckhead neighborhood because of the convenience and accessibility for both clients and employees the firm also announced the addition of three senior hires carly e howard senior vice president and senior wealth strategist atlanta bret a farris cfp cima senior vice president and business development officer chicago and bradley fincher senior vice president and business development officer florida carly howard joins the atlanta team with  years of industry experience previously she worked in bbt wealths professional and executive advisory group in charlotte north carolina providing customized wealth management services for executives and business owners with a focus on fiduciary issues related to executive compensation bret farris joins the chicago office with more than  years of industry experience prior to joining atlantic trust he was a senior client advisor at bmo private bank where he served as a business development and lead relationship manager focused on client retention and new client acquisition and led a team of subject matter experts to coordinate and execute personalized solutions for clients and prospects bradley fincher represents atlantic trust in the firms west palm beach office and has more than  years of industry experience prior to joining atlantic trust fincher was a vice president at bernstein private wealth management where he provided clients guidance on various investment wealth transfer tax planning and philanthropic strategies similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states t partners llc united states jumpcom inc united states  ontario inc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target no transactions available in the past  months request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global market intelligence directly by clicking here stock quotes market data is delayed at least  minutes company lookup most searched private companies company name geographic region lawyers committee for civil rights under law united states nyc inc united states the advertising council inc united states bertelsmann ag europe rush university united states sponsored financial commentaries sponsored links browse companies a b c d e f g h i j k l m n o p q r s t u v w x y z              request profile update only a company representative may request an update for the company profile documentation will be required to contact atlant